org.grouplens.lenskit.symbols

Class TypedSymbol<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.symbols.TypedSymbol<K>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class TypedSymbol<K>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A symbol associated with a particular type. Conceptually, each type can have a collection of symbols associated with it; that association is represented represented by this class.
    Since:
    1.3
    See Also:
    Symbol, Serialized Form

    Compatibility: Public
